<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.3">
<l>valli yiṭaiyāḷ poruṭṭāka matiḷnī rilaṅkai yārkōvai</l>
<l>yallal ceytu veñcamattu ḷāṟṟal mikutta vāṟṟalāṉ</l>
<l>vallā ḷarakkar kulappāvai vāṭa muṉitaṉ vēḷviyai</l>
<l>kalvic cilaiyāl kāttāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city of the strong one</l>
<l rend="indent">whose strength surged in heated battle,</l>
<l>Creating torment for the king of those of Laṅkā, with the sea as fortification,</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the creeper-waisted lady,</l>
<l>The one who with a [well-] practiced bow protected the sacrifice of the sage</l>
<l>So that the maid of the clan of demon strongmen perished.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
